    "description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/ac03c46bee201fd6fc87f13be1732dff.avif?t=1770317972\" width=954 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/de4c578951be40a4b33d8470cd9932e3.poster.avif?t=1770317972\" width=608 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/de4c578951be40a4b33d8470cd9932e3.webm?t=1770317972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/de4c578951be40a4b33d8470cd9932e3.mp4?t=1770317972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >世界上的某些区域被时间循环的魔法所笼罩。走上几步后，你将被送回到进入的地方。探索这个世界的规则，看看它们能带你走多远。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/408282d50afec84a32be5486ca656c9f.avif?t=1770317972\" width=954 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"> <br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/4c4c0da3c4e9edfe40a9536183afdfc1.poster.avif?t=1770317972\" width=608 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/4c4c0da3c4e9edfe40a9536183afdfc1.webm?t=1770317972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/4c4c0da3c4e9edfe40a9536183afdfc1.mp4?t=1770317972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >每个谜题都经过精心设计，用来教你一条新的世界规则。没有无意义的任务或重复劳动，只有纯粹的规则发现与思维挑战体验。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/b3ee042804753c57f926d959a3b49c08.avif?t=1770317972\" width=954 height=120 /></span></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" style=\"text-align: center\"><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/5d7bb76338c472a9bc1460d2a88e2f08.poster.avif?t=1770317972\" width=608 height=204 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/5d7bb76338c472a9bc1460d2a88e2f08.webm?t=1770317972\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3220700/extras/5d7bb76338c472a9bc1460d2a88e2f08.mp4?t=1770317972\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >你的进度只受限于你的知识，而非人为的解锁机制。曾经看似不可能的事情，也许只需要你再仔细看看。没错，你其实从一开始就能做到！</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>主要特色：</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>独特的谜题设计</strong> - 通过创造性地操控局部时间循环来解谜。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>基于知识的探索与进展</strong> - 在这个世界中，你唯一的限制就是你所了解的知识。</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>秘密与元谜题</strong> - 跳出思维定势，解开层层相连、相互影响的谜题。</p></li></ul>",
